It can also do normal women just fine, but that isn't what you're here for, is it?

Standard settings work fine. All example images are unedited and use the standard settings.

For the negative, I usually go with:

lowres, low res, text, error, cropped, worst quality, low quality, normal quality, jpeg artifacts, artist signature, watermark, text, username, blurry, out of focus, censored, out of frame, b&w, mask, selfie, 3d, sketch, cartoon, extra arms,

For a starting prompt, I'd recommend this:

Then start generating and see what works for you.
